IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. HELLO-WORLD.
AUTHOR .HAWIN.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-INPUT PIC 9(3) .
01 WS-I PIC 9(3) VALUE 1.
01 WS-FACTORIAL PIC 9(15) VALUE 1.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
ACCEPT WS-INPUT.
PERFORM UNTIL WS-I > WS-INPUT
  COMPUTE WS-FACTORIAL=WS-FACTORIAL * WS-I
  ADD 1 TO WS-I
END-PERFORM.
DISPLAY "FACTORIAL IS: " WS-FACTORIAL.

STOP RUN.
